後告唔告得入唔係最重要，目的係令多啲人有權拎CCTV，還原真相⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 98190979<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權觀察 94632945<br />\n伍展邦律師行 26081400<br />\n<br />\n推呀！！唔想有人抄車，但更加唔想抄左車但冇人知！！黑警一定要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！啦<br />\n<br />\n想自保都有野幫到手!<br />\n如果想自保，請所有知情人士立即錄影一片短片(遮樣，但一定要仔細描述當時情況)，將你所知既細節送去各大媒體，並響9月5日中午12點前，以匿名方式送到各大媒體(報章、社交媒體)。當呢件事徹底曝光，響公眾既注視下，你地先會真正既安全<br />\n<br />\n知道你地可能有好多各方面擔心 但想知真相得一個方法 就係拎到cctv 唔想搞民氏訴訟 都幫手拍條片send去各大媒體啊<br />\n求下你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡力幫幫手<br />\n如果拎到 我地離革命成功 又遇進一大步ga啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70353b104c4c62b1dfa2191112948e01e8000bf1","tid":1542412,"uid":41961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"係咪林奠搭高鐵上廣西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5327ed7f1788f1caaaf7543f552ecad4514cf19","tid":1542412,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:30:44.000Z","msg":"武警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4272965a054c9ff875808c516b74fb506836ba","tid":1542412,"uid":75668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=